<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08149a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08149a">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08149a"> 149(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ perpetual fire put / out by arbp. D. <font color="green">[1200]</font> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Firehouse. In the fifth/sixth century, St Brigid founded a monastery in Kildare. This contained a firehouse, a circular fenced enclosure, where a perpetual fire was kept burning. It was finally quenched by order of De Londres, Archbishop of Dublin, in 1220, but was soon relit and kept burning until the Dissolution of the Monasteries. </mm> </dd></dl>
